NUMBER 2677
NAME Kentaurus Boulevard
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
Large, majestic mansions line this boulevard that connects to Park Street.
Wrought iron fences surround the estates, guarding the demesnes from
unwanted intrusion. Through many of the fences one can see immaculate
gardens of multi-colored flowers that lend a bright cheeriness to the
entire street. At the end of the street can be seen a large vine-covered
arch, with the Greycloak symbol proudly displayed on top.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT S 270
ITEM 0 60 ADJ1=178
EXTEND 0 covered with blooming vines
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
While the arch does not contain a gate to keep intruders out, you get the
sense that magic is involved in the security of the Greycloak estate.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB GO 0
  CLEARVERB
   IFVAR INTNUM40 = 33
     ECHO PLAYER You pass through the arch.
     ECHO OTHERS %P passes through the arch.
     MOVEGROUP 2678
     AFFECT 2678
     ECHO OTHERS %P comes through the arch.
     AFFECT 2677
     ELSE
     ECHO PLAYER The vines covering the arch form an impenetrable barrier.
     ECHO OTHERS The vines covering the arch form an impenetrable barrier as %N attempts to pass through it.
   ENDIF
ENDIF
