NUMBER 2678
NAME Greycloak Estate, outside
OUTDOOR_OTHER
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
Flowers and bushes line a circular path that leads from a leafy arch to
the front door of the Greycloak mansion. In the center of the circle is
an emerald green patch of vibrant grass, upon which sits a beautiful
marble fountain. The fountain shoots streams of crystal clear water from
its top, glittering with a golden light in the nighttime. Closely cropped
hedges line the cobblestoned path leading to the oak front door.
*DESCRIPTION_END
