NUMBER 2692
NAME Hot Tub
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
The tub itself is immaculately clean. A soft magical light glows dimly over
the polished mirmach tub walls. The sides of the tub have been magically
softened to ensure a comfortable and luxuriant time. A panel of buttons is
set into the wall to one side of the tub.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT O 2691
ITEM 0 247 ADJ1=29
ITEM 1 247 ADJ1=347
VARIABLE whitten
VARIABLE whitten1
IFENTRY
  IFVAR whitten = 0
    ECHO PLAYER There is no water in the tub at this moment.
  ENDIF
  IFVAR whitten = 1
    ECHO PLAYER The tub is filled with steaming and bubbling water that soothes your aching muscles.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB PUSH 0
  ADD whitten 1
  IFVAR whitten = 1
      ECHO ALL %N pushes the blue button and the tub fills with hot, soothing warm water that bubbles luxuriantly all over your body.
      AFFECT 2691
      ECHO ALL Wispy clouds of steam rise from the tub as hot water fills its interior.
      AFFECT 2692
  ENDIF
  IFVAR whitten = 2
    SUB whitten 2
      ECHO ALL %N pushes the blue button and you watch the water drain quickly out of the tub.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB PUSH 1
 ADD whitten1 1
 IFVAR whitten1 = 1
  ECHO ALL The strains of Ravel's Bolero emanate from hidden speakers and fill the room.
 ENDIF
  IFVAR whitten1 = 2
    ECHO ALL The last lyrical note of Ravel's Bolero hangs in the air for a moment and then fades away.
    EQUAL whitten1 0
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB SIT -1
  IFVAR whitten = 1
    ECHO ALL %N sits down, leaning against the soft, padded walls of the tub, causing some of the hot water to splash over the side.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB WAVE -1
  IFVAR whitten = 1
    ECHO OTHERS %N splashes water at you.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB LISTEN -1
  IFVAR whitten1 = 1
    ECHO PLAYER The sensous music of Ravel's Bolero flows through your body, combining with the water to wash all of your troubles away...
  ENDIF
ENDIF
