NUMBER 2693
NAME Patio
DAY_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
Carefully placed red bricks form the floor of this large patio. Enclosed
by the two wings of the mansion the patio offers respite from any wind while
still allowing pleasant sunlight to wash warmly over the entirety of this
outside area. The patio leads out over a lush grass carpet that slowly
fades into the beautiful oaken trees that surround Fayd's city park.
*DESCRIPTION_END
